</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB45618FFFBFF9CFF6EFEACFAD37F6D" blockId="5.[208,1379,269,350]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<keyLead id="30FAF52DFFFBFF9CFF6EFEACFAD37F6D" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
— Plantes prostrées à feuilles à limbes ovés-aplatis (présence très douteuse en 
<collectingCountry id="F31C1688FFFBFF9CFC43FEACFB7D7F71" box="[1021,1229,298,322]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">Nouvelle-Calédonie</collectingCountry>
, voir note à ce sujet dans l’introduction) 
<emphasis id="B97F8A0AFFFBFF9CFDB0FEC1FB877F6D" box="[526,1079,327,350]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">...................................................................................</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C0B2D9BFFFBFF9CFBFFFEC0FAD37F6D" authority="Sw." authorityName="Sw." box="[1089,1379,326,350]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Dendrobium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="5" pageNumber="156" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="linguiforme">
