</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30FF4EBDFFFBFF9CFF6EFEFCFAD17FF8" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<paragraph id="8BB45618FFFBFF9CFF6EFEFCFAD27F9D" blockId="5.[208,1378,378,459]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<keyLead id="30FAF52DFFFBFF9CFF6EFEFCFAD27F9D" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
2. Inflorescence pauciflore de 1-2 (-3) fleurs. Lobe médian du labelle arrondi. Tépales verts à vert jaunâtre ........ ........................................................................................................................ 
<taxonomicName id="4C0B2D9BFFFBFF9CFB92FE10FAD27F9D" authority="Benth." authorityName="Benth." box="[1068,1378,406,430]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Dendrobium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="5" pageNumber="156" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bowmanii">
<emphasis id="B97F8A0AFFFBFF9CFB92FE10FAA67F9D" box="[1068,1302,406,430]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">Dendrobium bowmanii</emphasis>
Benth.
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB45618FFFBFF9CFF6EFE32FAD17FF8" blockId="5.[208,1378,378,459]" box="[208,1377,435,459]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<keyLead id="30FAF52DFFFBFF9CFF6EFE32FAD17FF8" box="[208,1377,435,459]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">— Inflorescence multiflore de (4-)10 (-15) fleurs. Lobe médian du labelle aigu ................................................ 3</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30FF4EBDFFFBFF9CFF6EFE61FAD37CBD" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<paragraph id="8BB45618FFFBFF9CFF6EFE61FAD37C0B" blockId="5.[208,1379,487,654]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<keyLead id="30FAF52DFFFBFF9CFF6EFE61FAD37C0B" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
3. Labelle à lobe médian aigu, arqué, mais non défléchi. Lobes latéraux du labelle et colonne blancs (parfois légèrement teintés de rouge). Tépales blancs. Feuilles rainurées, (22-) 54-84 (-132) × (1-) 2-3 (-4) mm ................ ........................................................................................................................ 
<taxonomicName id="4C0B2D9BFFFBFF9CFB95FDA6FAD37C0B" authority="Schltr." authorityName="Schltr." box="[1067,1379,544,568]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Dendrobium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="5" pageNumber="156" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="casuarinae">
<emphasis id="B97F8A0AFFFBFF9CFB95FDA6FAA97C0B" box="[1067,1305,544,568]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">Dendrobium casuarinae</emphasis>
Schltr.
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB45618FFFBFF9CFF6EFDBBFAD37CBD" blockId="5.[208,1379,487,654]" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
<keyLead id="30FAF52DFFFBFF9CFF6EFDBBFAD37CBD" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">
— Labelle à lobe médian longuement acuminé, à acumen défléchi et enroulé sur lui-même. Lobes latéraux du labelle et colonne fortement marqués de rouge.Tépales jaune sale. Feuilles non rainurées, (90-)123-201(-253) × 1-2.5 mm .............................................................................................................. 
<taxonomicName id="4C0B2D9BFFFBFF9CFBECFDF0FAD37CBD" authority="Schltr." authorityName="Schltr." box="[1106,1379,630,654]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Dendrobium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="5" pageNumber="156" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vagans">
<emphasis id="B97F8A0AFFFBFF9CFBECFDF0FAA87CBD" box="[1106,1304,630,654]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="156">Dendrobium vagans</emphasis>
Schltr.
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
